        <li>destroyed_suffix-&gt;[to] ashes</li>
        <li>destroyed_suffix-&gt;[to] a cinder</li>
        <li>destroyed_suffix(recipient_flesh!=Mechanoid)-&gt;[to] an unrecognizable mess</li>
